    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Saga of Guardians</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saga of Guardians is a unique collectible card game and auto battler. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build YOUR deck, place your cards strategically and climb the ranks in the PVP Arena. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build the most powerful deck</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect  cards from 3 unique factions and discover the most powerful synergies to overcome your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Place your cards strategically</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200210/extras/18e92b14facb6a3fa769256d48df0d50.poster.avif?t=1755158774\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200210/extras/18e92b14facb6a3fa769256d48df0d50.webm?t=1755158774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200210/extras/18e92b14facb6a3fa769256d48df0d50.mp4?t=1755158774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble and power up your team, predict your opponents move and defeat their Guardian.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle phase auto resolves</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200210/extras/e6de48dbb9e393f45a4d90297c9705f7.poster.avif?t=1755158774\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200210/extras/e6de48dbb9e393f45a4d90297c9705f7.webm?t=1755158774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200210/extras/e6de48dbb9e393f45a4d90297c9705f7.mp4?t=1755158774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you have given your commands it's up to your team. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the fight play out and use that information to play out your next turn.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Collect cards</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200210/extras/52517a2f24e07fffcef91f95a7f6f04d.poster.avif?t=1755158774\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200210/extras/52517a2f24e07fffcef91f95a7f6f04d.webm?t=1755158774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200210/extras/52517a2f24e07fffcef91f95a7f6f04d.mp4?t=1755158774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect over 150 unique cards from 3 different factions!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Prove yourself</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play in the arena against player from all over the world and climb the ladder! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
